  "title": "Agent Skills",
  "content": "Lovart Skills are intelligent workflows tuned for specific creative tasks. When you pick a Skill, the Agent knows what it needs to produce, asks you for anything missing, and moves through the steps automatically to deliver a finished output. Unlike a free-form prompt, a Skill encodes prompt best practices, professional design guidelines, and multi-step chains, so you can follow the Agent's lead.\n\nAvailable Skill Categories\n\nCustom Skills distill any conversation into a reusable Skill, so you can rerun the same workflow on new inputs without prompting from scratch. Use it to lock in a process you've already proven, and build a personal library of workflows over time.",
